===English===

===Noun===

'''hypocorism'''
 
===Etymology===

Late Latin '''hypocorisma''', from Greek (hypokorisma), from (hypokorizesthai) 'to call by pet names', from ([[hypo]]-) + (korizesthai) to [[caress]], from (koros) [[boy]], (kore) [[girl]]

===Meaning===

#a pet name
#the use of pet names 

===Adjectives===

:'''hypocoristic'''  
:'''hypocoristical'''

===Adverb===

:'''hypocoristically'''